\family typewriter
evidence_log(yt)
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

→
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

double
\family default
 returns logarithm of the 
\emph on
marginal likelihood
\emph default
 (sometimes also called 
\emph on
evidence
\emph default
)
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Smi:10"

\end_inset

 of the observation 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}$
\end_inset

, which is passed as 
\family typewriter
yt
\family default
 (
\family typewriter
vector
\family default
